2018.11-rc3, released November 30th, 2018

	Fixes all over the tree.

	Defconfigs: Fixes for Armadeus APF27, imx6sabre, Olimex A20
	olinuxino lime legacy, Orangepi zero plus 2, PC, Riotboard.

